Text: Thank you very much for this book Karaokeking! You are amazing!

I am wondering if you could please find some more Penny Vincenzi?  I believe she has written 14.

Also I am a Diana Gabaldon fan, so would love to see The Scottish Prisoner and Cross Stitch, which I believe are the only two missing now.

I would also like to say how much your hard work is appreciated.
Can you please upload this in PDF?? I would greatly appreciate it my eReader can't read mobi, epub or kk
can you please upload glass ? i can't find it anywhere.
